  "html": "<p class=\"\">I've always believed that if you're going to spend half your life in a terminal, it might as well feel like a cyberpunk movie. These tools explore how joy-drivem devex design can transform the routine into something that makes even doing your chores fun.</p>\n<p class=\"\">Each tool follows the Unix philosophy of doing one thing well, but with enough personality to make you smile when you run them.</p>\n<p class=\"\">They represent my approach to design: functionality first, but never underestimating the power of delight.</p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"featured-tools\">Featured Tools</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">Core Development Tools</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc\">\n<li class=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/ejfox/git-status-dash\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">git-status-dash<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385c.6.113.82-.258.82-.577c0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04c-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729c1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236c1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998c.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605c-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93c0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22c-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176c0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23c.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405c1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405c2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23c.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176c.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22c0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92c.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22c0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286c0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a>: Multi-repo git status dashboard with ASCII visualization</li>\n<li c